# 🎸 TabForge (Working Title)

**TabForge** is a modern, intuitive app that helps guitarists create, edit, and share tablature with ease. Designed for both beginners and advanced musicians, the app focuses on clean design, real-time playback, and smart editing features to speed up the tab-making process.

---

## 🚀 Features (Planned MVP)

- 🎼 **Tab Editor** with interactive fretboard
- 🔊 **Playback system** for tabs with adjustable tempo
- 📲 **Mobile-first interface** designed for quick edits
- 🧠 **Smart input** (auto-formatting, string detection)
- ☁️ **Cloud sync** (optional – local save by default)
- 🔗 **Export to PDF or share link**
- 🔒 No login required (for basic usage)

---

## 🧩 Tech Stack (Planned)

- **Frontend:** React Native / Flutter (TBD)
- **Backend:** Firebase / Supabase (for sync + storage)
- **Playback engine:** WebAudio / Tone.js
- **Data format:** JSON-based tab schema

---

## 👩‍🎤 Target Users

- Guitar students learning covers
- Songwriters who want fast draft tabs
- Guitar teachers giving tab homework
- Anyone annoyed by clunky old tab sites

